This map is ba_jail_tentcity_v2a
This map contains alot of features....One of my favorites along side from ba_jail_electricrazor

Some features this map contains is:
2 BigCages(1 inside/1 outside)
2 pits(1 pool inside/one gray one outside)
Armory
2 Cells(1 inside/1 outside)
Infirmary
Solitare
Small deathrun
Race with surf(crouch jumping and crouching and surf at end to win
In bigcage there is a corner box u can break in both of the BC
Trampoline
2 Towers outside for ct's
Armory consist of M4a1,Ak47,Deagle,Armor,Awp's
Has a climb thingy...(two sides...One pushes button and 3 beeps go and then starts first to top and pushes button wins)

I think this map is an all around good map.
